1
00:00:18,980 --> 00:00:24,420
♪It's a sordid story that you've made♪

2
00:00:26,700 --> 00:00:32,700
♪Up to fill my mind with doubts and pain♪

3
00:00:34,780 --> 00:00:40,220
♪Blood I shed, and tears I wept,
are you satisfied?♪

4
00:00:40,220 --> 00:00:42,540
♪Enjoying what's mine♪

5
00:00:42,540 --> 00:00:49,500
♪Have you found a way
to bury guilt and shame♪

6
00:00:50,540 --> 00:00:55,020
♪I'm coming back to life♪

7
00:00:55,020 --> 00:00:58,700
♪Through the seven gates of death♪

8
00:00:58,700 --> 00:01:02,820
♪I'm coming back survived♪

9
00:01:02,820 --> 00:01:06,580
♪Feeling great to see you fall♪

10
00:01:06,580 --> 00:01:10,820
♪I'm taking back what's mine♪

11
00:01:10,820 --> 00:01:15,340
♪Bringing horror to the battlefield♪

12
00:01:15,340 --> 00:01:19,060
♪Lay it to waste♪

13
00:01:19,060 --> 00:01:22,940
♪Til the day my kingdom is reclaimed♪

14
00:01:38,260 --> 00:01:42,540
=Her Blaze=

15
00:01:43,000 --> 00:01:45,974
=Episode 7=

16
00:01:57,367 --> 00:01:58,848
Dad.

17
00:02:00,367 --> 00:02:01,527
Look.

18
00:02:02,848 --> 00:02:05,608
You know all
of your daughter's secrets now.

19
00:02:07,888 --> 00:02:09,048
Back then,

20
00:02:10,967 --> 00:02:13,087
you once helped my mother and me.

21
00:02:14,775 --> 00:02:15,615
Today,

22
00:02:17,100 --> 00:02:19,019
could you help me one more time?

23
00:02:20,328 --> 00:02:22,768
Change the title deed to my name.

24
00:02:22,825 --> 00:02:24,105
Help me recover

25
00:02:24,448 --> 00:02:26,967
No. 88 Linwei Alley,
which belongs to me.

26
00:02:34,025 --> 00:02:38,275
(Salted Duck)

27
00:02:39,537 --> 00:02:40,417
Come back again!

28
00:02:40,417 --> 00:02:41,058
I will.

29
00:02:43,288 --> 00:02:44,087
Excuse me.

30
00:02:44,187 --> 00:02:45,187
Who is Bai Xia

31
00:02:45,187 --> 00:02:46,426
from No. 88 Linwei Alley?

32
00:02:46,700 --> 00:02:47,500
I am.

33
00:02:47,750 --> 00:02:50,208
A Ms. Bai asked us to deliver this.

34
00:02:50,208 --> 00:02:51,288
Please sign for it.

35
00:02:57,075 --> 00:02:58,625
(Electric Wheelchair)

36
00:03:01,650 --> 00:03:03,530
Could you help me move it
to the second floor?

37
00:03:03,575 --> 00:03:04,216
Sure.

38
00:03:05,212 --> 00:03:06,011
Thank you.

39
00:03:08,537 --> 00:03:09,338
Careful.

40
00:03:18,100 --> 00:03:21,237
(Property Ownership Certificate
of the People's Republic of China)

41
00:03:21,275 --> 00:03:22,775
(Salted Duck)

42
00:03:43,867 --> 00:03:45,228
(Kicking you out of Lysen Group)

43
00:03:46,707 --> 00:03:48,468
(is not my ultimate goal.)

44
00:03:49,910 --> 00:03:50,908
(I know you will surely)

45
00:03:50,908 --> 00:03:52,827
(try every means to come back.)

46
00:03:54,228 --> 00:03:55,267
(This game has just)

47
00:03:55,267 --> 00:03:56,508
(started its first round.)

48
00:03:58,068 --> 00:03:58,948
(Next,)

49
00:03:59,867 --> 00:04:01,228
(I'll make you feel)

50
00:04:01,230 --> 00:04:02,388
(the taste of desperately
gaining everything)

51
00:04:02,388 --> 00:04:04,068
(only to lose it all again.)

52
00:04:04,068 --> 00:04:07,362
(Xinkang Treatment Center: Rao Yuci)

53
00:04:16,037 --> 00:04:18,500
(Lin)

54
00:04:21,668 --> 00:04:22,747
(Linwei Alley)
(And Linwei Alley)

55
00:04:23,547 --> 00:04:25,228
(will be the beginning of your failure.)

56
00:04:25,228 --> 00:04:26,312
(Linwei Alley)

57
00:04:39,668 --> 00:04:40,468
You're here.

58
00:04:41,788 --> 00:04:42,588
Sit down.

59
00:04:42,975 --> 00:04:46,468
(Rongguangli, 24/7 Convenience Store)

60
00:04:46,468 --> 00:04:47,987
Boss, I'll take another soda.

61
00:04:47,987 --> 00:04:49,108
Sure, help yourself.

62
00:04:53,268 --> 00:04:54,387
Did you move out?

63
00:04:56,028 --> 00:04:56,828
No.

64
00:04:57,260 --> 00:04:59,570
I'm just temporarily staying
somewhere else for a few days.

65
00:04:59,588 --> 00:05:01,028
I'm keeping the house here.

66
00:05:03,228 --> 00:05:04,507
Why did you want to see me today?

67
00:05:08,210 --> 00:05:10,160
There's a letter
I wanted to give you in person.

68
00:05:10,268 --> 00:05:11,187
You can take a look.

69
00:05:18,588 --> 00:05:19,668
This is rare.

70
00:05:20,108 --> 00:05:21,108
The weather is so nice,

71
00:05:21,788 --> 00:05:22,987
and we can actually sit down

72
00:05:22,987 --> 00:05:24,307
and chat calmly.

73
00:05:24,588 --> 00:05:25,987
No fighting, no bickering.

74
00:05:29,867 --> 00:05:31,067
Why did you help me?

75
00:05:34,187 --> 00:05:35,228
Regarding Bai Liangliang,

76
00:05:36,708 --> 00:05:37,828
why did you help me?

77
00:05:41,427 --> 00:05:42,788
I just did what I should do.

78
00:05:47,828 --> 00:05:49,148
Who are you, exactly?

79
00:05:55,148 --> 00:05:56,310
I've left the letter for you.

80
00:05:57,320 --> 00:05:58,507
Read it if you're interested.

81
00:06:02,668 --> 00:06:03,908
Boss, I've paid.

82
00:06:03,908 --> 00:06:04,507
Alright.

83
00:06:04,507 --> 00:06:05,268
Take care.

84
00:06:10,908 --> 00:06:11,668
Ci,

85
00:06:11,668 --> 00:06:13,067
he often comes here to wait for you.

86
00:06:13,307 --> 00:06:14,307
He's a good boy.

87
00:06:14,307 --> 00:06:15,348
You should cherish him.

88
00:06:27,307 --> 00:06:28,108
(Rao Yuci,)

89
00:06:28,867 --> 00:06:31,387
(for you, your body is currently
recovering very quickly.)

90
00:06:32,427 --> 00:06:34,387
(The only side effect
is intermittent tremors.)

91
00:06:35,547 --> 00:06:36,788
(This is a normal phenomenon.)

92
00:06:37,500 --> 00:06:38,747
(With the change in medication,)

93
00:06:38,747 --> 00:06:40,067
(everything will get better.)

94
00:06:41,680 --> 00:06:43,187
(I know the nightmares torturing you)

95
00:06:43,187 --> 00:06:44,228
(follow you like a shadow.)

96
00:06:45,507 --> 00:06:46,348
(It seems)

97
00:06:47,588 --> 00:06:48,627
(you need a long time)

98
00:06:48,627 --> 00:06:49,747
(to find relief on your own.)

99
00:06:51,547 --> 00:06:53,108
(Someone needs to try)

100
00:06:53,668 --> 00:06:55,028
(to stand from your perspective)

101
00:06:55,500 --> 00:06:57,228
(and feel everything
you've encountered.)

102
00:06:58,108 --> 00:06:59,307
(One cannot judge easily,)

103
00:07:00,148 --> 00:07:01,788
(nor jump to conclusions lightly.)

104
00:07:03,668 --> 00:07:04,468
(However,)

105
00:07:04,468 --> 00:07:06,150
(24/7 Convenience Store)

106
00:07:06,187 --> 00:07:07,028
(I think you possess)

107
00:07:07,028 --> 00:07:08,348
(an astonishing strength.)

108
00:07:10,268 --> 00:07:11,307
(And this strength)

109
00:07:12,468 --> 00:07:13,747
(is exceptionally powerful.)

110
00:07:14,760 --> 00:07:15,708
(You don't seem to need)

111
00:07:15,708 --> 00:07:16,828
(anyone's help.)

112
00:07:18,028 --> 00:07:19,268
(You wrap yourself inside)

113
00:07:19,268 --> 00:07:20,547
(a hard shell.)

114
00:07:23,108 --> 00:07:23,908
(Rao Yuci,)

115
00:07:25,947 --> 00:07:26,908
(your kind of bravery)

116
00:07:26,908 --> 00:07:28,427
(24/7 Convenience Store)
(will affect those around you,)

117
00:07:28,487 --> 00:07:29,662
(Rao Yuci, if you have any needs,
feel free to call me.)

118
00:07:29,708 --> 00:07:30,427
(Rao Yuci, if you have any needs, feel free to call me.)
(making it impossible for them)

119
00:07:30,427 --> 00:07:31,788
(to pull away from your side.)

120
00:07:31,788 --> 00:07:33,337
(Rao Yuci, if you have any needs,
feel free to call me.)

121
00:07:33,387 --> 00:07:36,867
(Even it makes them want
to stay with you.)

122
00:07:38,708 --> 00:07:40,348
(You seem to have a magic)

123
00:07:41,725 --> 00:07:42,964
(that attracts others,)

124
00:07:44,708 --> 00:07:46,507
(even if this magic is dangerous.)

125
00:07:46,575 --> 00:07:48,987
(Shanghai Volunteer Association for Students and the Disabled,
Warm Heart Public Welfare Help Center)

126
00:07:48,987 --> 00:07:49,788
(I hope)

127
00:07:51,387 --> 00:07:52,348
(you can take a good)

128
00:07:52,348 --> 00:07:53,307
(look at this world.)

129
00:07:54,867 --> 00:07:56,228
(Please donate all the money)
(There are many corners of this world)

130
00:07:56,228 --> 00:07:56,947
(in this card to those in need.)
(that are not just about)

131
00:07:56,947 --> 00:07:58,228
(The password is on the back - Inanna)
(petty interests.)

132
00:08:00,708 --> 00:08:01,627
(There are still many)

133
00:08:01,627 --> 00:08:03,350
(exceptionally
happy things in this world.)

134
00:08:04,788 --> 00:08:05,588
(Yuci,)

135
00:08:07,427 --> 00:08:09,228
(if the past were a demon,)

136
00:08:11,400 --> 00:08:12,348
(I hope you would have)

137
00:08:12,348 --> 00:08:13,588
(the courage to defeat it.)

138
00:08:19,712 --> 00:08:24,012
(We take care of your heart)

139
00:08:49,708 --> 00:08:51,507
(Lysen Group)
It's here. It's in locker two.

140
00:08:51,548 --> 00:08:53,147
Please sign for it here.

141
00:09:01,787 --> 00:09:03,188
Ms. Ren, yes?

142
00:09:03,667 --> 00:09:04,468
Mr. Jiang,

143
00:09:04,880 --> 00:09:07,308
all the materials for
the Linwei Alley Urban Renewal Project

144
00:09:07,308 --> 00:09:09,160
have been handed
over to Chen Xi from Dept 1.

145
00:09:10,588 --> 00:09:11,468
Alright.

146
00:09:24,948 --> 00:09:25,987
What are you doing?

147
00:09:25,987 --> 00:09:27,500
Who told you to move this? Put it down!

148
00:09:28,267 --> 00:09:29,387
We're moving things out.

149
00:09:32,507 --> 00:09:33,308
Ms. Chen,

150
00:09:33,548 --> 00:09:35,787
what exactly are you doing?

151
00:09:36,428 --> 00:09:37,228
Tina,

152
00:09:37,828 --> 00:09:39,348
now that Ms. Bai is gone,

153
00:09:41,068 --> 00:09:42,428
the feng shui of this room

154
00:09:42,428 --> 00:09:43,627
doesn't look very good.

155
00:09:43,747 --> 00:09:44,548
So,

156
00:09:46,548 --> 00:09:48,228
I wanted to adjust it a bit.

157
00:09:48,747 --> 00:09:49,548
Ms. Chen,

158
00:09:49,787 --> 00:09:51,468
Ms. Bai is only on a temporary leave.

159
00:09:51,708 --> 00:09:52,507
Oh?

160
00:09:54,228 --> 00:09:55,027
Tina,

161
00:09:55,548 --> 00:09:56,987
didn't you get the notice?

162
00:09:57,428 --> 00:09:59,188
I am in charge of Dept 1 now.

163
00:09:59,667 --> 00:10:01,468
And from what I've heard Mr. Jiang say,

164
00:10:02,027 --> 00:10:03,760
it seems he doesn't
want her to come back.

165
00:10:05,588 --> 00:10:06,387
Keep moving.

166
00:10:07,228 --> 00:10:08,027
Wait a minute.

167
00:10:12,188 --> 00:10:12,987
Ms. Chen,

168
00:10:13,907 --> 00:10:14,588
these are all

169
00:10:14,588 --> 00:10:16,068
Ms. Bai's personal belongings.

170
00:10:16,360 --> 00:10:17,907
Even if you really intend to move them,

171
00:10:17,987 --> 00:10:19,548
you should at least inform her first.

172
00:10:27,987 --> 00:10:28,787
Hello?

173
00:10:28,800 --> 00:10:30,308
Have you reached the airport, Ms. Bai?

174
00:10:30,600 --> 00:10:32,360
You must have
started your vacation by now.

175
00:10:32,907 --> 00:10:33,987
What's your point?

176
00:10:34,308 --> 00:10:36,188
It's the style of your office.

177
00:10:36,387 --> 00:10:37,228
Every time I come in,

178
00:10:37,228 --> 00:10:38,907
it makes me feel very uncomfortable.

179
00:10:39,507 --> 00:10:41,027
Since you've left,

180
00:10:41,708 --> 00:10:42,507
I thought

181
00:10:42,987 --> 00:10:44,588
I'd change the style.

182
00:10:45,228 --> 00:10:46,228
Don't worry.

183
00:10:46,787 --> 00:10:47,828
As for your things,

184
00:10:47,948 --> 00:10:48,787
I've put them all in

185
00:10:48,787 --> 00:10:50,068
the Dept 3 storage room.

186
00:10:50,480 --> 00:10:51,987
You can come and pick them up anytime.

187
00:10:53,948 --> 00:10:55,108
Who said I'm leaving?

188
00:10:55,987 --> 00:10:56,787
What?

189
00:10:57,150 --> 00:10:58,570
You still haven't given up, Ms. Bai?

190
00:10:58,588 --> 00:10:59,667
Don't forget,

191
00:11:00,108 --> 00:11:01,267
the Linwei Alley

192
00:11:01,267 --> 00:11:02,548
Urban Project you had

193
00:11:02,548 --> 00:11:04,267
was given to you by Rao Yuci.

194
00:11:04,548 --> 00:11:05,348
Can't you see

195
00:11:05,348 --> 00:11:06,708
who you should really be wary of

196
00:11:06,708 --> 00:11:07,747
and dealing with right now?

197
00:11:08,428 --> 00:11:10,468
Chen Xi, you'd better carefully consider

198
00:11:10,468 --> 00:11:11,948
what your next move should be.

199
00:11:11,948 --> 00:11:13,667
That has nothing
to do with you, Ms. Bai.

200
00:11:16,667 --> 00:11:18,068
Ms. Chen, do we keep moving them?

201
00:11:27,112 --> 00:11:28,267
Put everything back.

202
00:11:40,627 --> 00:11:41,507
He's here.

203
00:11:42,867 --> 00:11:44,068
Manager...

204
00:11:45,228 --> 00:11:46,267
Yuci said

205
00:11:46,907 --> 00:11:48,348
we should all have a meal together.

206
00:11:50,507 --> 00:11:51,468
I have a date.

207
00:11:52,387 --> 00:11:53,548
Keep my portion.

208
00:11:53,987 --> 00:11:56,147
And get a few more fans

209
00:11:56,468 --> 00:11:57,708
for the Dept 3 office.

210
00:12:00,348 --> 00:12:01,147
Miss Meng.

211
00:12:02,948 --> 00:12:04,308
I have plans with my husband.

212
00:12:04,747 --> 00:12:05,708
Let's do it another day.

213
00:12:08,588 --> 00:12:09,387
Tian Tian,

214
00:12:10,068 --> 00:12:10,867
in Lysen,

215
00:12:11,588 --> 00:12:12,828
you need to use your head.

216
00:12:20,548 --> 00:12:21,348
Tian Tian,

217
00:12:21,828 --> 00:12:22,627
I'll treat you.

218
00:12:25,188 --> 00:12:25,987
Yuci.

219
00:12:28,662 --> 00:12:32,550
(Linwei Alley BBQ)

220
00:12:32,600 --> 00:12:35,400
(Linwei Alley BBQ)

221
00:12:48,507 --> 00:12:49,308
Careful.

222
00:12:51,937 --> 00:12:53,458
Nuan is much more cheerful than before.

223
00:12:55,787 --> 00:12:57,880
She's been following us,
running around everywhere.

224
00:12:58,068 --> 00:12:59,627
She rarely has playmates.

225
00:12:59,627 --> 00:13:00,787
Since coming to this street,

226
00:13:00,787 --> 00:13:01,708
Lin here

227
00:13:01,787 --> 00:13:03,188
has been playing with her.

228
00:13:03,747 --> 00:13:04,548
Lin,

229
00:13:04,627 --> 00:13:06,147
come, let's go back

230
00:13:06,228 --> 00:13:07,068
and sit for a while.

231
00:13:09,627 --> 00:13:10,428
Go play.

232
00:13:15,548 --> 00:13:17,747
Dr. Chen, what a coincidence.

233
00:13:34,027 --> 00:13:34,828
Mr. Chen.

234
00:13:35,267 --> 00:13:36,108
Mr. Chen,

235
00:13:37,228 --> 00:13:39,108
can you help translate this for Nuan?

236
00:13:39,188 --> 00:13:40,428
She can't read many words yet.

237
00:13:40,787 --> 00:13:42,308
This is my hometown address.

238
00:13:42,308 --> 00:13:42,900
(Shitou Village, Yingyang County)

239
00:13:42,907 --> 00:13:43,867
(Shitou Village, Yingyang County)
Tell Nuan

240
00:13:44,308 --> 00:13:45,387
that after I leave,

241
00:13:45,747 --> 00:13:47,068
she can come here to find me.

242
00:13:47,468 --> 00:13:48,708
I'll be waiting for her.

243
00:13:49,068 --> 00:13:50,708
This is my dad's phone number.

244
00:13:52,210 --> 00:13:54,480
So, are you going back to your hometown
to go to school?

245
00:13:54,787 --> 00:13:55,787
My dad said

246
00:13:56,507 --> 00:13:58,948
this place is going to be demolished
to build skyscrapers.

247
00:13:59,000 --> 00:14:00,790
- It's being demolished?
- We have to leave.

248
00:14:06,627 --> 00:14:10,348
(She wants you
to find her at this address.)

249
00:14:28,068 --> 00:14:31,228
Boss, does this entire street
have to be demolished?

250
00:14:31,387 --> 00:14:32,188
Yes.

251
00:14:32,310 --> 00:14:34,188
The demolition notice
has already been issued.

252
00:14:34,308 --> 00:14:35,068
All of us

253
00:14:35,068 --> 00:14:36,627
are gradually moving our things out.

254
00:14:38,050 --> 00:14:39,930
Where will you go after this?

255
00:14:41,027 --> 00:14:42,428
In such a big city,

256
00:14:42,747 --> 00:14:44,428
there will surely be a place for us.

257
00:15:24,468 --> 00:15:25,267
Everyone,

258
00:15:26,068 --> 00:15:27,108
friends,

259
00:15:30,588 --> 00:15:32,267
let me introduce myself.

260
00:15:32,348 --> 00:15:33,627
My name is Li Quanyou,

261
00:15:34,308 --> 00:15:35,987
from Fuyang, Anhui.

262
00:15:36,787 --> 00:15:39,468
I'm the owner of this Malatang shop.

263
00:15:40,667 --> 00:15:42,228
Many of my old customers

264
00:15:42,708 --> 00:15:44,308
and old friends are here today.

265
00:15:45,108 --> 00:15:46,147
I remember you all.

266
00:15:47,027 --> 00:15:48,588
When you were in university,

267
00:15:48,588 --> 00:15:49,828
you'd come here

268
00:15:50,507 --> 00:15:51,708
to eat Malatang

269
00:15:52,708 --> 00:15:53,987
and secretly date.

270
00:15:55,027 --> 00:15:57,747
And now you're married with children.

271
00:15:58,147 --> 00:15:59,308
After all these years,

272
00:16:00,188 --> 00:16:01,948
Linwei Alley Snack Street

273
00:16:02,667 --> 00:16:04,548
has left us all

274
00:16:05,267 --> 00:16:07,108
with beautiful shared memories.

275
00:16:07,348 --> 00:16:08,147
Right?

276
00:16:08,348 --> 00:16:10,747
- Yes!
- That's right!

277
00:16:12,348 --> 00:16:15,507
Many of my old neighbors are here.

278
00:16:16,147 --> 00:16:16,948
Qing.

279
00:16:17,787 --> 00:16:19,228
Roasted gluten is unmatched!

280
00:16:19,708 --> 00:16:22,867
Brother Qiang from the stir-fry shop.

281
00:16:24,428 --> 00:16:26,387
And the Fruit Bowl owners,

282
00:16:26,747 --> 00:16:28,507
Nuan's parents.

283
00:16:29,787 --> 00:16:30,987
In a few days,

284
00:16:31,507 --> 00:16:32,787
we'll be moving away.

285
00:16:34,588 --> 00:16:35,308
I think today,

286
00:16:35,308 --> 00:16:36,907
many old friends

287
00:16:38,108 --> 00:16:38,987
knew the snack street

288
00:16:38,987 --> 00:16:40,627
is about to be demolished,

289
00:16:41,188 --> 00:16:42,348
so they came to check in

290
00:16:43,147 --> 00:16:44,308
and keep a memory.

291
00:16:44,828 --> 00:16:45,987
But mostly,

292
00:16:48,188 --> 00:16:49,428
we just can't bear to let go.

293
00:16:56,712 --> 00:17:01,862
♪Raise a glass
and drink away the faded past♪

294
00:17:02,025 --> 00:17:06,837
♪Goodbye to the way we used to be♪

295
00:17:07,212 --> 00:17:12,562
♪Youth was just a dream
that came and went♪

296
00:17:12,637 --> 00:17:17,512
♪The roads we walked together
won't fade away♪

297
00:17:17,912 --> 00:17:23,100
♪I don't know why
we rush through every day♪

298
00:17:23,237 --> 00:17:28,275
♪Yet hope still lives inside my heart♪

299
00:17:28,375 --> 00:17:33,820
♪Whenever we recall our younger days♪

300
00:17:34,062 --> 00:17:40,237
♪Our friendship never fades away♪

301
00:17:50,268 --> 00:17:51,828
I read the letter you wrote me.

302
00:17:54,828 --> 00:17:55,627
Thank you.

303
00:18:03,308 --> 00:18:04,187
Thank you

304
00:18:05,788 --> 00:18:06,907
for telling me all this.

305
00:18:07,867 --> 00:18:08,667
It's nothing.

306
00:18:11,028 --> 00:18:11,988
After a major illness,

307
00:18:12,387 --> 00:18:14,068
people always need to start over.

308
00:18:15,828 --> 00:18:16,988
Start over.

309
00:18:17,100 --> 00:18:19,350
♪My whole heart
has fallen out of control♪

310
00:18:19,387 --> 00:18:20,348
Before starting over,

311
00:18:20,348 --> 00:18:21,907
there are so many things to do.

312
00:18:23,962 --> 00:18:27,162
♪Before I learn to live without you♪

313
00:18:27,227 --> 00:18:28,108
Ms. Bai Xia.

314
00:18:29,147 --> 00:18:30,308
You're back, Yuci.

315
00:18:32,308 --> 00:18:33,108
This is...

316
00:18:33,748 --> 00:18:34,548
My friend.

317
00:18:36,907 --> 00:18:37,828
I'll let you two talk.

318
00:18:37,828 --> 00:18:38,947
I'm heading back first.

319
00:18:43,907 --> 00:18:45,147
I live here now.

320
00:18:46,068 --> 00:18:47,508
No. 88 Linwei Alley.

321
00:18:49,467 --> 00:18:50,108
Is this also

322
00:18:50,108 --> 00:18:51,588
part of your starting over?

323
00:18:55,988 --> 00:18:56,788
Yes.

324
00:19:01,467 --> 00:19:02,308
Have you thought

325
00:19:02,308 --> 00:19:03,627
about what things would be like

326
00:19:04,720 --> 00:19:06,420
if you gave up everything
you want to do?

327
00:19:08,308 --> 00:19:09,028
Then, I would

328
00:19:09,028 --> 00:19:10,548
never be able to start over.

329
00:19:12,387 --> 00:19:13,187
I'm leaving.

330
00:19:16,712 --> 00:19:19,925
(Salted Duck)

331
00:19:27,337 --> 00:19:31,937
(Four years ago. Resume. Chen Mo.
Objective: Psychological Counselor.)

332
00:19:32,348 --> 00:19:33,348
Last question.

333
00:19:33,828 --> 00:19:35,268
As a psychological counselor,

334
00:19:35,268 --> 00:19:37,348
how do you think we should help patients

335
00:19:37,348 --> 00:19:38,788
at Xinkang Treatment Center?

336
00:19:39,800 --> 00:19:43,037
♪I fear this freedom I never asked for♪

337
00:19:43,068 --> 00:19:43,707
To be honest,

338
00:19:43,707 --> 00:19:44,988
I initially studied psychology

339
00:19:44,988 --> 00:19:46,187
to heal myself.

340
00:19:47,308 --> 00:19:48,068
You can imagine

341
00:19:48,068 --> 00:19:48,907
that inside everyone,

342
00:19:48,907 --> 00:19:50,028
there is a river.

343
00:19:50,907 --> 00:19:51,947
The water in that river

344
00:19:52,707 --> 00:19:54,187
is all of a person's inner problems.

345
00:19:55,707 --> 00:19:57,108
Studying psychology allowed me

346
00:19:59,467 --> 00:20:00,748
to find the source.

347
00:20:02,387 --> 00:20:03,068
I also hope

348
00:20:03,068 --> 00:20:04,588
to help others

349
00:20:05,187 --> 00:20:06,308
in the same way.

350
00:20:09,700 --> 00:20:14,362
♪I wish I could watch every view with you♪

351
00:20:14,837 --> 00:20:20,362
♪Oh, but sadly I'm only a friend♪

352
00:20:20,425 --> 00:20:26,420
♪You the moonlight of my soul♪

353
00:20:26,625 --> 00:20:32,380
♪I wish I could walk with you
till the end of time♪

354
00:20:32,987 --> 00:20:40,262
♪Nothing more,
I need just to stay by your side♪

355
00:21:04,828 --> 00:21:05,627
Mr. Jiang.

356
00:21:06,707 --> 00:21:08,828
This was sent up first thing
by Rao Yuci from Dept 3.

357
00:21:08,907 --> 00:21:09,988
She said it's a new project.

358
00:21:10,175 --> 00:21:12,100
(Linwei Alley Snack Street Renewal Plan)

359
00:21:17,227 --> 00:21:18,387
Do you need to see her?

360
00:21:20,907 --> 00:21:21,748
I got it.

361
00:21:22,867 --> 00:21:23,667
Mr. Jiang.

362
00:21:24,427 --> 00:21:25,508
Make me a cup of coffee.

363
00:21:25,627 --> 00:21:26,427
Understood.

364
00:21:34,588 --> 00:21:35,387
Rao Yuci,

365
00:21:36,508 --> 00:21:37,667
what is the meaning of this?

366
00:21:40,947 --> 00:21:41,588
(Linwei Alley Snack Street Renewal Plan)
Don't you think

367
00:21:41,588 --> 00:21:43,028
this is a bit too absurd?

368
00:21:43,508 --> 00:21:45,508
Investing in a project,
how is that absurd?

369
00:21:45,988 --> 00:21:47,308
Can't you even distinguish

370
00:21:47,308 --> 00:21:48,800
the trivial from
the significant anymore?

371
00:21:49,147 --> 00:21:50,627
Don't you have any basic standards?

372
00:21:51,068 --> 00:21:51,947
My basic standard

373
00:21:51,947 --> 00:21:53,147
is the project itself.

374
00:21:54,108 --> 00:21:55,108
Can it be profitable?

375
00:21:55,108 --> 00:21:56,147
Does it have potential?

376
00:21:56,707 --> 00:21:57,988
If it does, why not do it?

377
00:21:58,480 --> 00:22:00,788
Then explain to me,
how does this project make a profit?

378
00:22:00,988 --> 00:22:01,788
Manager,

379
00:22:02,667 --> 00:22:04,187
while this is a small project,

380
00:22:04,268 --> 00:22:05,308
it is part

381
00:22:05,308 --> 00:22:06,788
of the Linwei Alley urban plan.

382
00:22:07,627 --> 00:22:09,748
There are many
merchants in Linwei Alley.

383
00:22:10,308 --> 00:22:12,187
Business stops entirely
during demolition.

384
00:22:12,548 --> 00:22:13,588
Any unrest will have

385
00:22:13,588 --> 00:22:15,548
a major negative impact on Lysen.

386
00:22:17,028 --> 00:22:18,108
This proposal

387
00:22:18,308 --> 00:22:19,147
mainly addresses

388
00:22:19,147 --> 00:22:20,947
some follow-up relocation issues.

389
00:22:22,108 --> 00:22:22,988
I think

390
00:22:23,748 --> 00:22:25,675
it also counts as helping Mr. Jiang.

391
00:22:25,675 --> 00:22:27,108
Tian Tian, that's enough.

392
00:22:29,187 --> 00:22:30,907
Is Lysen a charity?

393
00:22:31,147 --> 00:22:32,707
As long as the procedures are legal,

394
00:22:32,707 --> 00:22:34,227
who cares about the follow-up?

395
00:22:36,108 --> 00:22:37,548
Does Dept 3 belong to you alone,

396
00:22:38,627 --> 00:22:39,427
Tian Tian?

397
00:22:39,988 --> 00:22:41,308
Does Dept 3 belong to you alone,

398
00:22:41,308 --> 00:22:42,108
Rao Yuci?

399
00:22:44,588 --> 00:22:46,028
You can be idealistic,

400
00:22:46,427 --> 00:22:48,068
but others want promotions and raises.

401
00:22:48,068 --> 00:22:49,280
They have families to support.

402
00:22:49,947 --> 00:22:51,348
They need to eat and make money!

403
00:22:53,268 --> 00:22:54,068
I don't agree.

404
00:22:54,200 --> 00:22:55,300
(Linwei Alley Snack Street Renewal Plan)

405
00:23:02,947 --> 00:23:03,748
Yuci.

406
00:23:05,387 --> 00:23:06,268
Yuci,

407
00:23:07,268 --> 00:23:08,988
I support you no matter what.

408
00:23:09,387 --> 00:23:10,788
If you need me to do anything,

409
00:23:10,788 --> 00:23:11,707
just let me know.

410
00:23:15,110 --> 00:23:16,387
Then, come meet someone with me.

411
00:23:16,427 --> 00:23:17,227
Okay.

412
00:23:23,387 --> 00:23:24,348
There are no brands.

413
00:23:24,988 --> 00:23:26,147
They're all small vendors.

414
00:23:26,707 --> 00:23:27,508
Think about it.

415
00:23:27,548 --> 00:23:29,348
Who would lease to them as a whole?

416
00:23:30,268 --> 00:23:31,068
Besides,

417
00:23:31,467 --> 00:23:32,788
you have additional requirements.

418
00:23:33,707 --> 00:23:34,907
I've looked for you.

419
00:23:35,147 --> 00:23:36,227
There isn't a single one.

420
00:23:37,268 --> 00:23:38,788
To be honest, Miss Rao,

421
00:23:39,427 --> 00:23:40,467
I've evaluated

422
00:23:40,588 --> 00:23:41,748
this project proposal.

423
00:23:43,627 --> 00:23:45,308
It's really impractical.

424
00:23:45,748 --> 00:23:46,548
I don't think

425
00:23:46,988 --> 00:23:47,788
any company

426
00:23:47,788 --> 00:23:48,828
would lease to you.

427
00:23:50,028 --> 00:23:50,788
Mr. Zhou, look.

428
00:23:50,788 --> 00:23:52,028
Would this place work?

429
00:23:53,562 --> 00:23:55,062
(Yinyu Commercial Building:
A New Chapter of Prosperity)

430
00:23:56,550 --> 00:23:57,025
(Boosting Your Business to New Heights)

431
00:23:57,262 --> 00:23:59,625
(High-end Commercial
and Office Environment)

432
00:23:59,675 --> 00:24:00,825
(140,000 sqm GFA,
Prime Location, Premium Quality)

433
00:24:05,200 --> 00:24:07,800
(Yinyu Commercial Building)

434
00:24:18,627 --> 00:24:20,427
Manager, these two are here to see you.

435
00:24:20,427 --> 00:24:21,387
Okay. Get back to work.

436
00:24:21,748 --> 00:24:22,548
Hello.

437
00:24:22,748 --> 00:24:23,828
Hello, Miss Rao.

438
00:24:24,348 --> 00:24:25,467
I've reviewed the documents.

439
00:24:25,467 --> 00:24:28,028
Are these merchants you mentioned
all from Linwei Alley?

440
00:24:28,028 --> 00:24:28,788
Yes.

441
00:24:29,387 --> 00:24:30,387
I'm here to find out

442
00:24:30,387 --> 00:24:32,227
about the rent requirements here.

443
00:24:33,227 --> 00:24:34,508
Currently, the monthly rent

444
00:24:34,508 --> 00:24:35,828
for each shop is 20,000.

445
00:24:38,308 --> 00:24:40,187
Well, if we have
a long-term partnership,

446
00:24:40,187 --> 00:24:41,627
could there be some discounts?

447
00:24:42,268 --> 00:24:43,227
What do you mean?

448
00:24:45,028 --> 00:24:46,028
Half the rent.

449
00:24:47,268 --> 00:24:48,548
Half the rent?

450
00:24:48,548 --> 00:24:49,387
Then, let me ask,

451
00:24:49,387 --> 00:24:50,788
what is the approximate

452
00:24:50,828 --> 00:24:52,427
daily turnover for these shops?

453
00:24:53,600 --> 00:24:55,028
Seven or eight hundred on good days.

454
00:24:55,028 --> 00:24:55,988
On bad days...

455
00:24:56,947 --> 00:24:58,427
A maximum daily turnover of 800

456
00:24:58,467 --> 00:25:00,748
means the monthly turnover
is only 24,000.

457
00:25:01,028 --> 00:25:02,828
That just barely covers our rent.

458
00:25:02,828 --> 00:25:03,548
Leaving aside

459
00:25:03,548 --> 00:25:04,627
the issue of our commission,

460
00:25:05,028 --> 00:25:06,548
how will they make a profit?

461
00:25:07,187 --> 00:25:07,988
Besides,

462
00:25:08,227 --> 00:25:09,627
we don't have plans

463
00:25:09,627 --> 00:25:11,108
to lease them out right now.

464
00:25:11,588 --> 00:25:12,748
I'm sorry, ladies.

465
00:25:13,068 --> 00:25:13,907
Please leave.

466
00:25:17,988 --> 00:25:18,788
Yuci,

467
00:25:19,310 --> 00:25:21,867
this building has been empty for a year,
yet they won't lease it.

468
00:25:22,108 --> 00:25:23,867
The manager had such an attitude too.

469
00:25:24,227 --> 00:25:26,268
They must not be short on money.

470
00:25:27,308 --> 00:25:28,588
Don't you find it strange?

471
00:25:29,068 --> 00:25:29,988
Look into

472
00:25:30,000 --> 00:25:32,450
the company and shareholders
behind this commercial building.

473
00:25:35,467 --> 00:25:37,650
The company name is

474
00:25:37,988 --> 00:25:39,227
(Shanghai Yinyu Technology Co., Ltd.)
Yinyu Technology.

475
00:25:40,427 --> 00:25:41,667
The largest shareholder is...

476
00:25:45,707 --> 00:25:46,667
Xian Pengyu.

477
00:25:50,600 --> 00:25:52,788
The relationship
between Xian Pengyu and Bai Liangliang

478
00:25:52,788 --> 00:25:53,588
is not simple.

479
00:25:53,947 --> 00:25:55,308
What's even stranger

480
00:25:55,387 --> 00:25:56,907
is that this Xian Pengyu holds

481
00:25:56,907 --> 00:25:58,108
no position at Yuanjian,

482
00:25:58,108 --> 00:25:58,988
yet he established

483
00:25:58,988 --> 00:26:00,748
a company called Yinyu Technology.

484
00:26:00,748 --> 00:26:02,250
A tech company that doesn't do tech,

485
00:26:02,260 --> 00:26:04,147
but invested in
a commercial building instead.

486
00:26:04,147 --> 00:26:06,660
The person hiding behind the scenes
who doesn't want to be found

487
00:26:07,988 --> 00:26:09,308
is our leverage.

488
00:26:09,787 --> 00:26:10,667
(Linwei Alley Snack Street Renewal Plan)

489
00:26:10,667 --> 00:26:12,548
Thirty-eight percent.

490
00:26:15,187 --> 00:26:15,988
Miss Meng,

491
00:26:15,988 --> 00:26:16,775
(Lysen Group)

492
00:26:16,788 --> 00:26:17,508
Rao Yuci

493
00:26:17,508 --> 00:26:19,108
really is a little genius.

494
00:26:19,788 --> 00:26:21,667
In just two short days, she produced

495
00:26:21,667 --> 00:26:23,508
such a detailed proposal.

496
00:26:24,988 --> 00:26:26,707
Actually, I think this project

497
00:26:28,268 --> 00:26:29,068
is okay.

498
00:26:31,068 --> 00:26:32,187
Aren't you a smart one?

499
00:26:32,348 --> 00:26:33,427
Listen to Manager Yu.

500
00:26:35,575 --> 00:26:39,937
(Linwei Alley Snack Street Renewal Plan)

501
00:26:39,988 --> 00:26:41,828
She hasn't changed a bit.

502
00:26:43,427 --> 00:26:45,748
You seem to know her very well, Ms. Bai.

503
00:26:47,028 --> 00:26:49,068
She's just a self-righteous hero.

504
00:26:49,867 --> 00:26:50,707
I think

505
00:26:52,108 --> 00:26:53,867
this money-losing project of hers

506
00:26:53,867 --> 00:26:56,190
will definitely make her
the laughingstock of the company.

507
00:26:57,748 --> 00:27:00,268
She abandoned the company's planned
Linwei Alley project

508
00:27:00,788 --> 00:27:01,467
just to push for

509
00:27:01,467 --> 00:27:03,028
a snack street renewal plan.

510
00:27:03,268 --> 00:27:04,907
Mr. Jiang is indeed very angry.

511
00:27:06,227 --> 00:27:07,108
So, Ms. Bai,

512
00:27:07,588 --> 00:27:09,467
you need to help Mr. Jiang

513
00:27:09,467 --> 00:27:11,560
secure the land
in the Linwei Alley area even more.

514
00:27:13,268 --> 00:27:15,187
But with your current status, Ms. Bai,

515
00:27:15,600 --> 00:27:17,960
how will you participate
in the Linwei Alley transaction?

516
00:27:19,147 --> 00:27:20,548
Don't worry, Miss Gao.

517
00:27:21,348 --> 00:27:22,788
I have my own ways.

518
00:27:24,588 --> 00:27:25,348
This is the ticket

519
00:27:25,348 --> 00:27:27,028
for this year's Chopin concert.

520
00:27:27,028 --> 00:27:28,867
Doesn't your son play the piano?

521
00:27:28,988 --> 00:27:29,988
Take it.

522
00:27:31,828 --> 00:27:32,707
Thank you, Ms. Bai.

523
00:27:39,000 --> 00:27:41,187
How come I heard
you've been short on cash lately?

524
00:27:41,627 --> 00:27:42,588
You should've told me.

525
00:27:42,588 --> 00:27:43,387
Don't be a stranger.

526
00:27:44,867 --> 00:27:45,748
The person you found

527
00:27:45,748 --> 00:27:47,268
isn't tight-lipped enough.

528
00:27:47,828 --> 00:27:49,788
It's just
that Linwei Alley project, right?

529
00:27:50,268 --> 00:27:52,187
From an investment perspective,

530
00:27:52,187 --> 00:27:53,308
I'm interested.

531
00:27:53,308 --> 00:27:54,770
How about this?
Send me your card number.

532
00:27:54,788 --> 00:27:57,268
I'll tell Finance to transfer
whatever amount you're missing.

533
00:27:58,627 --> 00:27:59,627
Money from Yuanjian

534
00:27:59,627 --> 00:28:01,187
doesn't feel right to hold.

535
00:28:01,427 --> 00:28:03,068
Mr. Jiang would mind, too.

536
00:28:05,760 --> 00:28:06,828
I really don't get you all.

537
00:28:06,828 --> 00:28:08,700
You always have to make things
so complicated.

538
00:28:09,068 --> 00:28:09,867
Alright.

539
00:28:10,308 --> 00:28:11,227
Same thing as always.

540
00:28:11,828 --> 00:28:12,748
Whenever you need it,

541
00:28:12,788 --> 00:28:13,707
call me anytime.

542
00:28:13,707 --> 00:28:14,308
For you,

543
00:28:14,308 --> 00:28:15,907
I'm on call 24/7

544
00:28:15,907 --> 00:28:17,147
to handle anything.

545
00:28:17,147 --> 00:28:17,867
Okay?

546
00:28:18,268 --> 00:28:19,467
Let's talk later.

547
00:28:33,387 --> 00:28:34,187
Let's go.

548
00:28:34,387 --> 00:28:35,268
Let's go inside.

549
00:28:35,588 --> 00:28:36,467
- Okay.
- Okay.

550
00:28:36,467 --> 00:28:37,420
- Let's go.
- Let's go.

551
00:28:42,947 --> 00:28:44,308
This place you picked is great, Yu.

552
00:28:44,308 --> 00:28:45,387
This open-plan floor...

553
00:28:45,707 --> 00:28:46,508
What do you think?

554
00:28:46,988 --> 00:28:48,108
Are you happy

555
00:28:48,508 --> 00:28:49,467
with the place I chose?

556
00:28:49,867 --> 00:28:51,308
It's great. It's fantastic.

557
00:28:51,308 --> 00:28:52,748
Have you decided yet, Pengyu?

558
00:28:53,147 --> 00:28:55,748
What method will you use
to pool our shares together?

559
00:28:55,750 --> 00:28:56,788
Let's wait a bit longer.

560
00:28:56,988 --> 00:28:57,748
I want to see

561
00:28:57,748 --> 00:28:58,907
what Lysen's next move is.

562
00:28:59,268 --> 00:29:00,068
Everyone,

563
00:29:00,308 --> 00:29:01,427
starting from today,

564
00:29:01,427 --> 00:29:02,147
this place

565
00:29:02,147 --> 00:29:04,450
will be the headquarters
for dealing with Jiang Dongchao.

566
00:29:04,707 --> 00:29:06,867
Mr. Pengyu, there's something
I need to tell you.

567
00:29:08,700 --> 00:29:10,268
Two girls came by a couple of days ago.

568
00:29:10,268 --> 00:29:11,788
They wanted to rent a few units
in the basement.

569
00:29:11,788 --> 00:29:12,667
I turned them down.

570
00:29:14,348 --> 00:29:16,387
Brother, since you already
turned them down,

571
00:29:16,387 --> 00:29:17,627
why are you even telling me about it?

572
00:29:17,627 --> 00:29:19,028
It was only after they left

573
00:29:19,030 --> 00:29:21,100
that I took a closer look
at their business cards.

574
00:29:21,348 --> 00:29:22,707
They're from Lysen.

575
00:29:24,637 --> 00:29:26,637
(Rao Yuci, Junior Analyst,
Investment Dept 3)

576
00:29:31,068 --> 00:29:32,427
Mr. Rao, it's been a long time.

577
00:29:32,427 --> 00:29:33,068
Yes.

578
00:29:33,348 --> 00:29:35,268
How have your investments
been doing lately?

579
00:29:36,907 --> 00:29:37,788
You know what?

580
00:29:38,028 --> 00:29:38,947
They're doing great.

581
00:29:40,387 --> 00:29:42,187
I just got back from out of town.

582
00:29:42,187 --> 00:29:43,667
I was planning
to ask you out for a meal,

583
00:29:43,667 --> 00:29:45,387
but you beat me to it.

584
00:29:45,788 --> 00:29:46,867
What a coincidence.

585
00:29:47,467 --> 00:29:49,147
Liangliang, I owe it all to you.

586
00:29:49,588 --> 00:29:51,588
My profits are doubling now.

587
00:29:51,947 --> 00:29:53,028
Congratulations.

588
00:29:54,867 --> 00:29:56,308
Well, I have to thank you.

589
00:29:56,467 --> 00:29:57,268
Liangliang,

590
00:29:57,387 --> 00:29:58,348
for the last five years,

591
00:29:58,548 --> 00:30:00,707
you've been helping me
make money through investments.

592
00:30:06,227 --> 00:30:07,028
Mr. Rao,

593
00:30:09,680 --> 00:30:11,387
Mrs. Rao asked me
to bring you some food.

594
00:30:12,667 --> 00:30:13,467
Just put it there.

595
00:30:21,028 --> 00:30:21,828
Mr. Rao,

596
00:30:23,227 --> 00:30:25,667
if you like investing in futures,

597
00:30:26,348 --> 00:30:27,308
you should look into

598
00:30:27,308 --> 00:30:28,227
this platform.

599
00:30:32,627 --> 00:30:34,800
Chuxia has a business partnership
with this platform.

600
00:30:35,028 --> 00:30:36,227
We've conducted

601
00:30:36,227 --> 00:30:37,907
a very detailed investigation into them.

602
00:30:37,910 --> 00:30:39,187
They have a good financial status,

603
00:30:39,187 --> 00:30:40,387
and their processes are formal.

604
00:30:40,788 --> 00:30:42,627
Their boss trusts us very much.

605
00:30:43,508 --> 00:30:46,147
If you're interested,

606
00:30:46,667 --> 00:30:48,108
I can put in

607
00:30:48,308 --> 00:30:49,268
a word with their boss.

608
00:30:49,600 --> 00:30:51,387
You can feel confident

609
00:30:51,387 --> 00:30:52,588
about investing your money.

610
00:30:54,147 --> 00:30:55,108
That one time,

611
00:30:55,467 --> 00:30:57,427
I made 500,000 in an instant.

612
00:30:57,748 --> 00:30:59,467
Liangliang, in the future,

613
00:30:59,467 --> 00:31:00,788
if there are bigger projects,

614
00:31:00,947 --> 00:31:02,187
you must keep me in mind.

615
00:31:03,828 --> 00:31:05,147
There is one project actually,

616
00:31:06,988 --> 00:31:09,667
but the investment amount
is quite large.

617
00:31:10,187 --> 00:31:11,147
How large is it?

618
00:31:16,627 --> 00:31:17,427
Have a look.

619
00:31:17,637 --> 00:31:19,725
(Linwei Alley Urban Project: Plan for
Building a New Smart Commercial Complex)

620
00:31:33,427 --> 00:31:34,548
Like I said,

621
00:31:34,907 --> 00:31:35,867
never mind, Mr. Rao.

622
00:31:35,867 --> 00:31:37,348
Don't bother looking at this project.

623
00:31:37,348 --> 00:31:38,028
Liangliang,

624
00:31:38,548 --> 00:31:39,548
I'm just asking you,

625
00:31:39,788 --> 00:31:40,707
is this project

626
00:31:41,068 --> 00:31:42,348
reliable or not?

627
00:31:42,828 --> 00:31:44,268
Of course it's reliable.

628
00:31:44,867 --> 00:31:46,627
Linwei Alley
is a piece of land that Bosi

629
00:31:46,627 --> 00:31:47,988
and Lysen are both fighting for.

630
00:31:48,707 --> 00:31:49,467
If you have time,

631
00:31:49,467 --> 00:31:50,828
you can go see the site yourself.

632
00:31:54,520 --> 00:31:55,988
The funding required for this project

633
00:31:55,988 --> 00:31:57,467
is indeed quite large.

634
00:31:58,828 --> 00:32:01,707
Actually, we don't need that much.

635
00:32:02,050 --> 00:32:03,907
As long as we buy up
the dozen or so households

636
00:32:03,907 --> 00:32:05,308
in Linwei Alley

637
00:32:05,308 --> 00:32:06,227
before Lysen does,

638
00:32:06,467 --> 00:32:08,348
once Lysen takes over the purchase,

639
00:32:08,348 --> 00:32:10,490
we'll easily make a profit
from the price difference.

640
00:32:11,748 --> 00:32:12,548
Alright.

641
00:32:13,387 --> 00:32:14,187
Liangliang,

642
00:32:15,028 --> 00:32:16,147
let me think about it.

643
00:32:16,788 --> 00:32:18,227
Of course. Take your time.

644
00:32:38,310 --> 00:32:39,867
Where did you go so early this morning?

645
00:32:40,867 --> 00:32:41,947
I went to see a friend.

646
00:32:43,000 --> 00:32:44,308
I didn't know you were coming back,

647
00:32:44,308 --> 00:32:45,308
so I didn't cook.

648
00:32:45,308 --> 00:32:46,068
It's fine.

649
00:32:46,227 --> 00:32:47,308
I've already eaten.

650
00:32:49,548 --> 00:32:50,348
Zhaohe,

651
00:32:50,988 --> 00:32:51,788
after the company

652
00:32:51,788 --> 00:32:53,147
Yuci and the others owned

653
00:32:53,387 --> 00:32:54,748
was sold,

654
00:32:54,828 --> 00:32:56,387
is Yuci's share of the money

655
00:32:56,548 --> 00:32:57,907
with you?

656
00:32:59,348 --> 00:33:00,147
Why?

657
00:33:01,467 --> 00:33:03,227
The money is just sitting there.

658
00:33:03,300 --> 00:33:04,960
Wouldn't it be better
to earn some profit?

659
00:33:05,387 --> 00:33:06,667
That is Yuci's money.

660
00:33:07,108 --> 00:33:08,147
We can't touch it.

661
00:33:09,268 --> 00:33:10,508
We're her parents.

662
00:33:10,867 --> 00:33:12,108
Given her current situation,

663
00:33:12,108 --> 00:33:14,548
what's wrong with us
helping her make some money?

664
00:33:15,907 --> 00:33:17,147
She's already been discharged.

665
00:33:17,147 --> 00:33:17,707
Then,

666
00:33:17,707 --> 00:33:19,068
why hasn't she come home?

667
00:33:23,707 --> 00:33:24,508
Maybe

668
00:33:27,667 --> 00:33:29,467
she doesn't know how to face us.

669
00:33:30,707 --> 00:33:32,050
So she's staying out for now.

670
00:33:34,828 --> 00:33:36,748
I've already asked the treatment center.

671
00:33:37,308 --> 00:33:38,667
She has recovered.

672
00:33:38,947 --> 00:33:40,427
And I've seen her too.

673
00:33:40,748 --> 00:33:41,828
She's doing very well.

674
00:33:41,828 --> 00:33:43,147
It's only been three years,

675
00:33:43,588 --> 00:33:44,548
and she's recovered?

676
00:33:45,508 --> 00:33:46,268
Have you forgotten

677
00:33:46,268 --> 00:33:47,707
how she hurt you before?

678
00:33:48,187 --> 00:33:49,707
"It's only been three years"?

679
00:33:52,268 --> 00:33:53,387
Our daughter disappeared

680
00:33:53,387 --> 00:33:54,627
from our lives for three years.

681
00:33:55,620 --> 00:33:58,320
She stayed in that treatment center
all by herself for three years.

682
00:33:58,548 --> 00:34:00,427
Do you have any idea how she felt?

683
00:34:02,068 --> 00:34:02,907
Rao Shusheng,

684
00:34:03,707 --> 00:34:04,788
don't forget,

685
00:34:05,788 --> 00:34:06,748
you are her father.

686
00:34:06,748 --> 00:34:07,867
You are her dad!

687
00:34:07,867 --> 00:34:09,428
I just want what's best for this family.

688
00:34:09,430 --> 00:34:11,790
I don't want what happened
three years ago to happen again.

689
00:34:13,868 --> 00:34:15,227
She is our daughter.

690
00:34:15,627 --> 00:34:16,428
She was just...

691
00:34:18,187 --> 00:34:19,747
She was just sick.

692
00:34:34,548 --> 00:34:36,108
She was just sick.

693
00:34:51,812 --> 00:34:55,187
(Chuxia, Investment Dept 1, Lysen Group)

694
00:34:55,227 --> 00:34:57,068
(They say life is a gamble.)

695
00:34:57,747 --> 00:34:59,588
(Participants bet with their fate.)

696
00:34:59,588 --> 00:35:01,487
(Investment Dept 1)

697
00:35:01,548 --> 00:35:02,388
(Bai Liangliang,)

698
00:35:03,520 --> 00:35:04,548
(will you place your bets)

699
00:35:04,548 --> 00:35:05,468
(Yuanjian Capital)
(on Bai Muran)

700
00:35:05,468 --> 00:35:07,267
(or on Xian Pengyu?)

701
00:35:07,500 --> 00:35:09,187
(Lysen Group)

702
00:35:09,187 --> 00:35:11,267
(And Jiang Dongchao
has an irreconcilable grudge)

703
00:35:11,267 --> 00:35:12,988
(against Xian Pengyu's family.)

704
00:35:14,787 --> 00:35:15,908
(Who is the strong one?)

705
00:35:16,988 --> 00:35:18,548
(Who will be the final winner?)

706
00:35:20,988 --> 00:35:22,227
(If you must gamble,)

707
00:35:23,508 --> 00:35:25,548
(then be the one
standing at the highest point,)

708
00:35:25,588 --> 00:35:26,388
This way, please.

709
00:35:26,428 --> 00:35:27,868
(overlooking the entire situation.)

710
00:35:31,388 --> 00:35:33,227
Mr. Pengyu, Rao Yuci is here.

711
00:35:35,548 --> 00:35:36,388
Miss Rao,

712
00:35:36,868 --> 00:35:38,428
we finally meet.

713
00:35:45,012 --> 00:35:48,500
=Episode 7=
(The Gamble)

714
00:35:49,140 --> 00:35:51,580
(All animals in this production
were treated humanely)

715
00:35:51,580 --> 00:35:57,780
♪Take a breath and swallow
the words you couldn't say♪

716
00:35:58,540 --> 00:36:01,740
♪No need to force your heart anymore♪

717
00:36:01,740 --> 00:36:06,260
♪Searching for the season
we once missed♪

718
00:36:06,260 --> 00:36:13,780
♪Leave this place,
though wounded still stay strong♪

719
00:36:13,780 --> 00:36:17,700
♪You must believe
one day the rain will fall♪

720
00:36:17,700 --> 00:36:21,740
♪And wash away the mud
that stains your soul♪

721
00:36:21,740 --> 00:36:25,260
♪Find your freedom in the wild♪

722
00:36:25,260 --> 00:36:29,220
♪Take your stride and move ahead♪

723
00:36:29,220 --> 00:36:33,380
♪I will stay behind
and wait for your eyes♪

724
00:36:33,380 --> 00:36:37,580
♪To rebuild
the same flesh and soul again♪

725
00:36:37,580 --> 00:36:41,380
♪Wander freely through the thorns♪

726
00:36:41,380 --> 00:36:45,460
♪Keep walking through the light♪

727
00:36:45,460 --> 00:36:49,660
♪Fate is absurd, don't stop for anyone♪

728
00:36:49,660 --> 00:36:55,980
♪What you dare to lose
will one day be your own♪

729
00:37:13,100 --> 00:37:19,740
♪I'm sorry, I still owe you these words♪

730
00:37:19,740 --> 00:37:23,580
♪An apology that came too late♪

731
00:37:23,580 --> 00:37:28,220
♪Yet it's also the path
that saves my soul♪

732
00:37:28,300 --> 00:37:35,700
♪When the cold wind
passes it takes the past away♪

733
00:37:35,700 --> 00:37:39,780
♪You must believe and stand unwavering♪

734
00:37:39,780 --> 00:37:43,860
♪There will be hands
to pull you from the deep♪

735
00:37:43,860 --> 00:37:47,860
♪Find your freedom in the silence♪

736
00:37:47,860 --> 00:37:51,620
♪Let your wounds be mended♪

737
00:37:51,620 --> 00:37:55,820
♪Gray is not the past
and pain is not a shame♪

738
00:37:55,820 --> 00:37:59,980
♪Sometimes the sunlight
makes the world look crueler♪

739
00:37:59,980 --> 00:38:03,700
♪Wander through the echoes of regret♪

740
00:38:03,700 --> 00:38:07,740
♪Be forgiven and be sheltered♪

741
00:38:07,740 --> 00:38:11,780
♪After everything shatters,
hold my hand♪

742
00:38:11,780 --> 00:38:17,980
♪A flower reborn
will finally bloom forever♪
